name: Seattle Trails App
tagline: Explore Seattle's amazing trails with mobile apps.
body:
## Welcome to Seattle Trails apps.

### Privacy

Seattle Trails does not share or store any user information outside of the app. If you share media through the app with Twitter or Facebook, please refer to those companies privacy policies.

### Support or Contact
For support send an email to Chukundi.Salisbury@seattle.gov and we will get you in touch with the appropriate member of our team.
